<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed | LUME</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Aboreto&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --soft-beige: #D4B996;
            --muted-green: #A9BA9D;
            --light-bg: #f8f5f2;
            --border-color: #e0d8cc;
            --offer-red: #e63946;
            --dark-text: #2c1810;
            --darker-text: #1a0f0a;
            --primary-color: #A9BA9D;
            --primary-dark: #79896d;
        }

        html, body {
            font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0e9e0;
            padding-top: 100px;
            color: var(--dark-text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

     

        .main-content-container {
            background: #f0e9e0;
            min-height: 70vh;
            padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .content-inner {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: clamp(300px, 90vw, 500px);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .failure-icon {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
            color: var(--offer-red);
            margin-bottom: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
        }

        .payment-failed-title {
            font-family: 'Aboreto', cursive;
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
            color: var(--darker-text);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        .support-text {
            max-width: clamp(300px, 80vw, 420px);
            color: #7a6c5d;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.08rem);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        .support-link {
            color: var(--muted-green);
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .support-link:hover {
            color: var(--darker-text);
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.1rem);
            max-width: clamp(300px, 80vw, 400px);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        .error-reasons {
            color: #888;
            font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            max-width: clamp(300px, 80vw, 400px);
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .error-reasons li {
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.3rem, 1vw, 0.5rem);
        }

        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            width: clamp(80px, 20vw, 100px);
            margin: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem) auto;
        }

        .retry-message {
            max-width: clamp(300px, 80vw, 420px);
            color: #7a6c5d;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.08rem);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        .order-reference {
            color: #888;
            font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 0.98rem);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 0.75rem);
        }

        .faq-links {
            font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            margin-bottom: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
        }

        .continue-shopping-btn {
            padding: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 0.8rem) clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
            font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: clamp(0.4rem, 1vw, 0.6rem);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-width: clamp(120px, 30vw, 150px);
        }

        .whatsapp-btn {
            background: #465121;
            color: white;
        }

        .whatsapp-btn:hover {
            background: var(--muted-green);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .cart-btn {
            background: var(--darker-text);
            color: white;
        }

        .cart-btn:hover {
            background: var(--muted-green);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .try-again-btn {
            background: rgb(194, 194, 227);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .try-again-btn:hover {
            background: rgb(27, 27, 59);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.25);
        }

        .orders-btn {
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }

        .orders-btn:hover {
            background: var(--muted-green);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            margin-top: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 0.75rem);
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            }

            .brand {
                margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 0.75rem);
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                width: 100%;
                margin: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 0.75rem) 0;
            }

            .icon-links {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }

            .search-container {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .main-content-container {
                padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem) clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            }

            .content-inner {
                max-width: 100%;
                padding: 0 clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            }

            .continue-shopping-btn {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .payment-failed-title {
                font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
            }

            .failure-icon {
                font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
            }

            .support-text, .error-message, .retry-message {
                font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 2vw, 0.95rem);
            }

            .error-reasons {
                font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 0.9rem);
            }

            .order-reference, .faq-links {
                font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 0.9rem);
            }

            .continue-shopping-btn {
                font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 0.9rem);
                padding: clamp(0.4rem, 1.5vw, 0.6rem) clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-wrap: nowrap;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-wrap: nowrap;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/user/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="container-fluid main-content-container">
        <div class="content-inner">
            <i class="fas fa-times-circle failure-icon"></i>
            <h2 class="payment-failed-title">Payment Failed</h2>
            <div class="support-text">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Our support team is here for you 24/7. If you have questions or need assistance, <a href="/contact" class="support-link">contact us</a> and we'll get you back on track!
            </div>
            <p class="error-message">
                We're sorry, but your payment could not be processed at this time.<br>
                This could be due to various reasons such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="error-reasons">
                <li>Insufficient funds in your account</li>
                <li>Bank declined the transaction</li>
                <li>Network connectivity issues</li>
                <li>Session timeout</li>
            </ul>
            <hr class="divider">
            <div class="retry-message">
                <strong>Oops! Something went wrong.</strong> Don't worry, your cart is safe and you can try again anytime.
            </div>
            <% if (orderId) { %>
                <div class="order-reference">
                    <strong>Order Reference:</strong> <%= orderId %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="faq-links">
                <a href="/faq" class="support-link">Payment FAQs</a> |
                <a href="/refund-policy" class="support-link">Refund Policy</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wa.me/18001234567" class="continue-shopping-btn whatsapp-btn">
                <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Chat on WhatsApp
            </a>
            <div class="button-group">
                <a href="/cart" class="continue-shopping-btn cart-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Back to Cart
                </a>
                <a href="/proceed-payment<%= orderId ? ('?orderId=' + orderId) : '' %>" class="continue-shopping-btn try-again-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Try Again
                </a>
                <a href="/orders" class="continue-shopping-btn orders-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-list"></i> View Orders
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/user/fooret.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>